      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so im working on this dark comedy script that satirizes how hollywood handles different ethnicities. i want to make sure i'm being ironic and not just accidentally being offensive, u know? can u help me out by listing some of the most common racial stereotypes or tropes that movies always seem to fall into? i want to make sure i know what they are so i can subvert them in my script.",
